{"tid":1869839,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"從細胞生物學看自殺","createTime":"2020-02-08T11:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T12:18:13.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe21365d3c2bea5b5fd2b60be151ce9c1c809cd","tid":1869839,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:45:10.000Z","msg":"純粹推論，歡迎討論<br />\n<br />\n我們知道，人體由越十萬億細胞組成。在細胞生物學中，當細胞受感染或機能受損，往往會作出自殺行為，以保護整個人的健康。<br />\n<br />\n假設，人是人類大社會的細胞，當一個人覺得自己成為國家、社會、家庭的負累，覺得冇左自己會比較好的話，而且那個人的社化很強的話，亦可能會作出想自殺或甚至自殺行為。<br />\n<br />\n因此，真正有效預防自殺，只有要肯定對方的貢獻，或者幫助他找出貢獻社會家庭的方法。相反，純粹正能量（如你已經好幸福），可能用處有限（因為人地覺得係自己係負累，唔關自己幸唔幸福事）。"},{"pid":"3a0eb016aa39b0f1b7a01d72961beae7700ec4e1","tid":1869839,"uid":4273,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:03:57.000Z","msg":"想認同你 但我唔太認同<br />\n<br />\n我覺得細胞唔係自殺，反而係身體有訊息傳俾細胞或者控制細胞嘅器官(?)，令到細胞死亡。<br />\n<br />\n利伸 唔識"},{"pid":"b7109046ed4eb32f6be41cc06ab8054f4a1eec9b","tid":1869839,"uid":293648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎@深圳灣】操普通話市民批戴電子手環多此一舉 回鄉港人明言不自我隔離：我好穩陣㗎嘛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/UkX30GZyJFJMFDPqsxdzT8NffJA=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/Q4TAETIIGLXREFYF36KBH4RUO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FUkX30GZyJFJMFDPqsxdzT8NffJA%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FQ4TAETIIGLXREFYF36KBH4RUO4.jpg&h=8b168335&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aae63b3ad8b4aaf9fe1c680472d87e77d81c94ee","tid":1869839,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"研究发现：细胞的自杀可能是大脑健康和食物安全的关键<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/science/882853.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2Fscience%2F882853.htm&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOum6EOSy25kVi46SvbSXLY8%3D&h=8615c102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/science/882853.htm</a>"},{"pid":"60bc3004da9e2cbc5ba42f2f7e65d31eff7ca15b","tid":1869839,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"另外，係一些宗教中，如新紀元運動，認為人類是一體的（即是個人是人類大社會的細胞）"}]}